<p>Good afternoon-  </p>
<p>I have browsed the forums as well as the web looking for an answer to this question. Hope someone out there can help.   </p>
<p>I need to create a .htaccess file that will only allow the files in the folder to be seen if the &quot;referer&quot; is from a particular site (or possibly two sites). I have found a lot of solutions out there for people who want to block specific sites, but I can't seem to figure out how to only allow specific sites. I have done some trial and error based on some of the things I have found, but with no luck.  </p>
<p>Any ideas?  </p>
<p>Thanks in advance!  </p>
<p>David</p>
